- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses the autonomy and intelligence of social robots. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper discusses the temporal profile of social robots and their purpose and application area. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is less likely but still possible as the paper briefly touches on the appearance of social robots.
